            .dropdown-menu(role='menu', aria-labelledby='navbarDropdown')
              a.dropdown-item(href='/workouts/new') Add Workout
        form.form-inline.my-2.my-lg-0
          button.btn.btn-outline-success.my-2.my-sm-0(type='submit') Graph
    .jumbotron.text-center
      img.logo(src='/images/Healthy-Lifestyle.jpg', alt='My_Logo')
      h1 Healthy Habits Reminder
      h4 How to Maintain a Healthy Lifestyle
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-4
          h3 Drink Water
          p
            | Drinking water is crucial to staying healthy and maintaining the function of
            | every system in your body, including your heart, brain, and muscles
          p
            | Fluids carry nutrients to your cells, flush bacteria from your bladder, and prevent constipation.
        .col-sm-4
          h3 Excerise
          p
            | Exercise can help keep your body at a healthy weight. Exercise helps people
            | lose weight and lower the risk of some diseases
          p
            | Exercising regularly decreases a person's risk of developing certain diseases,
            | including obesity, type 2 diabetes, and high blood pressure.
        .col-sm-4
          h3 Sleep Right
          p
            | Sleep plays an important role in your physical health as sleep is involved in
            | healing and repair of your heart and blood vessels
          p
            | Ongoing sleep deficiency is linked to an increased risk of heart disease,
            | kidney disease, high blood pressure, diabetes, and stroke.
    .container-fluid
      .row.content
        h3#title.container.raw Let's Track Your Daily Healthy Lifestyle
        .container.raw
          .form-check
